casebody.data:
No. 1123,

Misc.

Williams v. Zuckert, Secretary of the Air Force, et al. Sidney Dickstein, David I. Shapiro, Lawrence Speiser and Melvin Wulf for petitioner. Solicitor General Cox, Assistant Attorney General Orrick, Alan S. Rosenthal and Sherman L. Cohn for respondents.

Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit granted. Case transferred to the appellate docket.
